Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.68,0:00:21.49,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找尋著看不見的明天 著急地用手觸摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.64,0:00:25.99,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.15,0:00:38.55,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來是沒有出口的迷宮 就像需要解謎的拼圖一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.20,0:00:49.81,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有奇跡出現  夢想也將成為勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.05,0:00:54.98,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  在荏苒的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.13,0:00:57.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你的憧憬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.05,0:01:00.40,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  因為那份思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.56,0:01:03.69,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我了無形的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.98,0:01:09.80,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像稍微感受到了迷惘和煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.80,0:01:11.33,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論在什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.48,0:01:14.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  在荏苒的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.49,0:01:23.63,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  對你的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.67,0:01:28.64,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.12,0:21:41.39,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在心中綻放的玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.54,0:21:48.26,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗中燃盡  僅是一束火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.47,0:21:56.90,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在滿是隔閡的街上 如遊戲般的迷失自我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.03,0:22:01.12,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以小丑的心情躊躇著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.99,0:22:09.49,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要踐踏悲傷的殘片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.62,0:22:13.87,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人在未來中戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.42,0:22:21.97,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以解開今晚的謎底仍然是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.25,0:22:26.50,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up！真面目  Hurry up！回到從前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.79,0:22:33.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is passion　兩個人的手中充滿的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.14,0:22:40.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入黑暗之中   想緊緊擁抱住陽光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.40,0:22:46.50,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在迷宮中相互Kiss
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.65,0:22:55.58,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁向樂園  僅差一道門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.85,0:00:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨著時代的演進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.45,0:00:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,困難的案件也與日俱增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.15,0:00:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有二個人被殺害的恐怖事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.25,0:00:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一邊看片頭一邊來回顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.05,0:00:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.95,0:00:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.95,0:00:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,智慧卻過于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.25,0:00:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.27,0:01:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔 小蘭和我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.59,0:01:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被邀請去參加企業家的千金四井麗花的生日派對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.05,0:01:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是大家車子的輪胎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.25,0:01:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都遭到不明人士的破壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.05,0:01:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麗花小姐決定第二天等司機來接她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.75,0:01:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那幫馬屁精也都表示要跟她一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.05,0:01:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留在別墅住一個晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.95,0:01:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那天晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.75,0:01:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當大家正在尋找失蹤的麗花的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.95,0:01:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二階堂被溺死在噴水池那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.75,0:01:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小蘭也遭到同樣手法的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.05,0:01:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還好在千鈞一發之際被救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.95,0:02:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從兇手製造停電的手法來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.35,0:02:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以肯定兇手就是這棟別墅裡面的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.75,0:02:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在這個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.65,0:02:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,浸在浴室裡的麗花小姐的屍體被發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.65,0:02:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,企業家千金殺人事件(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.29,0:02:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.50,0:02:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.60,0:02:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她也是被溺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.70,0:02:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在檢查她喝下的水之前不能夠妄下結論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是根據我的推測
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.20,0:02:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她一定是頭部被強行按在浴缸裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.31,0:02:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,溺水而死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.01,0:02:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.11,0:02:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二階堂剛才在噴水池旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.98,0:02:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被人溺水致死的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.28,0:02:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及小蘭在廚房料理台旁被強行按入水中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.35,0:02:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,險些溺水身亡的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.58,0:02:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這兩件事件都是用的同一種手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.79,0:02:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.89,0:02:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.19,0:03:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無差別殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.10,0:03:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.20,0:03:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且這名兇手是一個非常殘暴的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.70,0:03:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們自己看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.90,0:03:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死者從裙子到襪子都濕透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.50,0:03:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也是麗花小姐她遇害的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.91,0:03:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曾經強烈反抗過的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.81,0:03:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.61,0:03:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不但如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.98,0:03:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的手腳上還有被捆綁過的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.38,0:03:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘴巴上面也有被膠帶貼過的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.58,0:03:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可見死者在被害之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.69,0:03:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是被兇手囚禁在什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.99,0:03:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.09,0:03:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是誰做了這麼過分的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.00,0:03:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才去上廁所的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.00,0:03:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是一枝叔叔 五條叔叔跟米嬸你們三個人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.70,0:03:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.90,0:03:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.00,0:03:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有注意到什麼可疑的人或者聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.91,0:03:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.61,0:03:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們其中一個人在上廁所的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.71,0:03:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外兩個人則在廁所外面等著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.98,0:03:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不記得發生過什麼怪事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.78,0:03:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等到一枝先生最後一個上廁所的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.28,0:04:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他要我和米嬸一起到廚房去泡咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.95,0:04:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後發生了什麼事情就不知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.29,0:04:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.39,0:04:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你是用這種方法製造了殺害麗花小姐的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.10,0:04:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泡咖啡至少需要5、6分鐘的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.90,0:04:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有了這段很充裕的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你表面上假裝在上廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.20,0:04:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實是到你囚禁麗花小姐的浴室裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.41,0:04:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把她殺了 對不對一枝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.41,0:04:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的 我才不是兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.18,0:04:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兇手的確不是一枝先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從麗花小姐屍體的情況來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.69,0:04:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她被殺害的時間離現在至少有一、兩個小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.19,0:04:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說犯罪時間 是在早上5點到6點之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.69,0:04:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從他上廁所的時間來判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.90,0:04:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不可能是殺人兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.50,0:04:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同樣的道理 五條先生和米嬸也都不可能行兇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.40,0:04:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為一枝你們三個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.70,0:04:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在早上4點到7點之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.31,0:04:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直和我一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待在客廳裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.18,0:05:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣一來他們就有了不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.98,0:05:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嫌疑人的範圍自然就縮小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.38,0:05:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的就是那段時間獨自留在二樓房間裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三船先生和六田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.35,0:05:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只可能是你們兩個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.09,0:05:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話就太簡單了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.40,0:05:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人兇手就是六田這個老小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.50,0:05:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為不可能是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.60,0:05:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你胡說 我明明看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.00,0:05:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凌晨6點的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.50,0:05:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你離開了房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.91,0:05:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道去哪裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.71,0:05:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎 三船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.68,0:05:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我睏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.88,0:05:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以就走到二樓的洗手間去洗臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.48,0:05:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.98,0:05:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二樓的洗手間就在樓梯的旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.89,0:05:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就更方便走到一樓去殺害麗花小姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.99,0:05:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說得也有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.39,0:05:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的行動的確沒有人證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.70,0:05:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你也一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在二樓房間裡的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同樣也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.30,0:05:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到過你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.71,0:06:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總而言之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.71,0:06:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯罪時間是在早上5點到6點之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.71,0:06:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以有可能犯案的只有你們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.38,0:06:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩你們兩位告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.58,0:06:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時候你們在哪裡 在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毛利叔叔說得很對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.79,0:06:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死亡的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.69,0:06:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確是在早上5點到6點之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.39,0:06:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.50,0:06:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最有嫌疑的果然就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.45,0:06:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那兩個人中的一個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.60,0:06:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.40,0:06:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼衣服會這麼濕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.81,0:06:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她再怎麼抵抗也不至於這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.41,0:06:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,膠帶的印子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.98,0:06:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兇手在用繩子綁住以後還用了膠帶嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.48,0:06:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼六田先生你從4點到7點之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.69,0:06:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直待在房間裡沒有出來過嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.99,0:06:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三船先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.29,0:06:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只有從房間裡出來過一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.09,0:06:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是到洗手間去洗臉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.10,0:07:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麗花小姐她到底是被囚禁在什麼地方的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.80,0:07:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是覺得不對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才我們每個房間都很仔細地找過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.51,0:07:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是都沒有看到她的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.81,0:07:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們大家尋找麗花小姐的時間是在10點左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.48,0:07:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時候在浴室裡什麼都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.58,0:07:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 浴缸裡面也是空的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是說在別墅外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說是在樹林裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.79,0:07:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對 如果是在別墅之外的話有個地方更合適
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.09,0:07:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是車子的行李箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.20,0:07:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是當時停在別墅前的你們幾位的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.40,0:07:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.10,0:07:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有時間把麗花小姐從行李箱裡搬出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.51,0:07:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也只有三船和六田先生兩個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.81,0:07:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.81,0:07:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個兇手就在你們兩位當中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.48,0:07:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們當中有一個是不分青紅皂白的殺人魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.48,0:07:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無差別殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.38,0:07:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實際上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小蘭雖然跟兇手素昧平生但也遭到攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.59,0:07:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家會這樣推測也無可厚非
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.49,0:08:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是為什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.69,0:08:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兇手為什麼不直接殺掉麗花小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.40,0:08:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反而把她囚禁起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.90,0:08:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直到現在才讓大家發現屍體呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.40,0:08:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麗花小姐是在浴室被殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.21,0:08:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果真的如叔叔所說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.61,0:08:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麗花小姐是先被囚禁在行李箱裡面的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.21,0:08:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兇手為什麼不在噴水池就殺了她呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.58,0:08:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣不但不會引人注目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.48,0:08:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不需要花那麼多時間在浴缸裡放水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.49,0:08:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.79,0:08:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕 蓮蓬頭噴出水來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.59,0:08:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蓮蓬頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.59,0:08:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.70,0:08:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是兇手使用的時間差的詭計
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.90,0:08:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的衣服之所以會濕成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,屍體上留下的膠帶痕跡 以及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.61,0:08:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小蘭也遭到攻擊的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.21,0:08:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有他故意拖延屍體被發現的時間的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.58,0:08:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一切的謎底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.98,0:08:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都串成一條線了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.49,0:09:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話兇手恐怕就是那個傢伙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.99,0:09:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能用這種手法攻擊小蘭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.05,0:09:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也只可能是那個混蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.79,0:09:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 還沒有證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能證明他就是兇手的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.60,0:09:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 到底還缺少些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.05,0:09:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.85,0:09:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看把自己弄得那麼濕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.00,0:09:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弄濕？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.71,0:09:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之 大家在車子來接我們之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.68,0:09:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就在客廳裡等吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.58,0:09:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也很擔心在那裡休息的小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.58,0:09:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.99,0:09:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次又怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.59,0:09:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...剛才不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.49,0:09:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要開始了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.45,0:09:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...怎麼了 偵探先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.20,0:09:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道兇手是誰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.10,0:09:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.81,0:09:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兇手嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.21,0:09:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家請把外套脫掉統統丟到我這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.41,0:09:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就真相大白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.08,0:10:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有完沒完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.98,0:10:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.98,0:10:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就照偵探先生說的做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.19,0:10:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說只要檢查一下外套就知道犯人是誰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.69,0:10:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧 你快點看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.05,0:10:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是說看了外套就知道了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.01,0:10:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想得沒錯 果然是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.85,0:10:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在別墅裏犯下三件案件的兇手就是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.05,0:10:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先在噴水池那裡把二階堂溺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.15,0:10:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著用安眠藥把昏睡的小蘭帶到廚房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.96,0:10:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差點也把她溺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.76,0:10:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後是這次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.06,0:10:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把麗花小姐溺死在這個浴缸裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.86,0:10:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個兇手就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.37,0:10:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是你　一枝先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.07,0:11:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一枝 真的是你做的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.94,0:11:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別開玩笑了　偵探先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.94,0:11:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看起來像是殺人狂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.55,0:11:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先是第一件案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.25,0:11:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是在二階堂被殺之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.25,0:11:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一起到樹林裡去尋找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.75,0:11:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失蹤的麗花小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.35,0:11:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時候和二階堂在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.36,0:11:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是六田和一枝你們兩個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.66,0:11:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.76,0:11:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你們走進樹林後沒多久就分散開去找人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.17,0:11:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一枝先生單獨一個人後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.27,0:11:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就跟在二階堂的後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把他叫到噴水池那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.94,0:11:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你當時很可能對他說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.64,0:11:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在噴水池附近看到了麗花小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.74,0:11:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後從背後襲擊在噴水池旁邊的二階堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.05,0:11:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把他給溺死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.05,0:11:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那只是你的想像而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.25,0:11:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同樣的事也可能是六田做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.55,0:11:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且 攻擊二階堂和大小姐還不奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.96,0:11:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我為什麼又一定要攻擊小蘭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.16,0:12:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和小蘭今天是第一次見面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.66,0:12:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且兇手在攻擊小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.27,0:12:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把電閘拉掉的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.77,0:12:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就和你待在一起的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.27,0:12:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時候我怎麼可能去把電閘拉掉嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.74,0:12:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照你這麼說難道我還有共犯嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.34,0:12:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 就算你沒有什麼共犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.74,0:12:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電閘還是可以自動拉掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.25,0:12:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要利用這個別墅裏的空調和微波爐就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.75,0:12:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方法很簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.76,0:12:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先用遙控器把空調都設定在同一時間啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.26,0:12:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後又把這個啟動時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.26,0:12:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同樣地設定在廚房的微波爐上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.17,0:12:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣的話時間一到電器線路就會超負荷運轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.77,0:12:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當負荷升到了最高值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.34,0:12:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電閘就會自動跳開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.64,0:12:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個證據就是遙控器上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.24,0:12:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還顯示著斷電時的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斷電的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.25,0:12:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南還聽到了怪聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.75,0:12:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吧 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.55,0:13:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時候我聽到"叮"的一聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.06,0:13:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這裡的微波爐是撥盤調時間的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.46,0:13:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算停電了計時器也可以正常運作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.16,0:13:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我碰到微波爐的時候它還是熱的 不會錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.77,0:13:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.07,0:13:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你用這個方法讓別墅斷電之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.47,0:13:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在黑暗中把窗戶玻璃打破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.14,0:13:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我們以為兇手已經逃到外面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.54,0:13:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我們一群人全部追到別墅外面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.05,0:13:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後你就把落單的小蘭帶到廚房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.15,0:13:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想用同樣的方法溺死她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.65,0:13:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了讓她無法反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.15,0:13:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就事先在咖啡裡面放了安眠藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.16,0:13:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在別墅斷電前不久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.86,0:13:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你假裝和我一起找麗花小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.86,0:13:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而進了廚房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.26,0:13:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後你趁我離開廚房的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.27,0:13:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偷偷地把微波爐啟動也不是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.94,0:13:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你先等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.64,0:13:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你忘了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.14,0:13:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有不在場證明的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.14,0:13:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你應該記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.35,0:13:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是大小姐她被殺的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明明一直待在你身邊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.25,0:14:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有完美的不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.05,0:14:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果說這三起案子都是我一個人搞出來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.16,0:14:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你給我解釋清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.16,0:14:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我殺掉麗花小姐的方法是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.06,0:14:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得一枝說得很有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.26,0:14:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麗花小姐的死亡時間是在早上五點到六點之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.47,0:14:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是一枝他從四點到七點的這三個小時裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.07,0:14:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明就一直和我們在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.97,0:14:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有就是在小蘭喝的咖啡裡放安眠藥這件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.74,0:14:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米嬸把咖啡端到客廳的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.04,0:14:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們明明是隨便拿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.55,0:14:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.05,0:14:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他怎麼可能事先在咖啡裡放安眠藥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.15,0:14:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定一不小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.25,0:14:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就被他自己喝下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.35,0:14:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實這個道理非常簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.86,0:14:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他自己只要不喝就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.66,0:14:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是小蘭那杯咖啡也是隨便拿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.26,0:14:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他怎樣才能預測小蘭拿哪杯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.57,0:14:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為他根本就沒有必要預測
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.97,0:14:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安眠藥誰喝了都無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.94,0:14:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的意思是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.74,0:14:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也有可能是被害的對象嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.84,0:15:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你運氣差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.94,0:15:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喝下那杯咖啡的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.24,0:15:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在藥力的影響下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.45,0:15:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身體不能自由行動的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.05,0:15:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是男是女都不重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.15,0:15:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.15,0:15:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都會遭遇到和小蘭一樣的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.15,0:15:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道真的是無差別殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.66,0:15:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要亂說好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像我真的是殺人狂一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.06,0:15:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我真的是殺人狂的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.16,0:15:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就會在停電的一瞬間下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.36,0:15:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.56,0:15:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你從一開始的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.97,0:15:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就沒有殺掉小蘭的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.47,0:15:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你犯下第二次案件所要得到的不是誰的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.14,0:15:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是一段證詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.94,0:15:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想得到的證詞是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.84,0:15:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兇手的殺人手法是把被害人強行按到水裡將其溺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.35,0:15:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要得到這段證詞就可以讓我們認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.05,0:15:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論是麗花小姐被殺的案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.75,0:15:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是第一起或第二起案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.35,0:15:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被害人都是被兇手用暴力按入水中溺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.46,0:15:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.86,0:15:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麗花小姐不是溺死的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.66,0:15:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是被溺死的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.77,0:16:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是並不是被兇手硬生生地按到水裡溺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.14,0:16:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你們不覺得奇怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.54,0:16:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麗花小姐失蹤的時候是在晚上十點左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.94,0:16:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是被害卻是在早上五點到六點之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.55,0:16:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兇手為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.75,0:16:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要過七、八個小時才把她殺掉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.05,0:16:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且麗花小姐的衣服濕成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.76,0:16:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算她再怎麼反抗也不至於濕成那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.06,0:16:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外兇手為什麼把麗花小姐綁住後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.06,0:16:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還要用膠帶固定住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.97,0:16:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解開這些謎題的答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.77,0:16:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在這個蓮蓬頭上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.97,0:16:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蓮蓬頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.14,0:16:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通常在洗澡放水的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.54,0:16:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該從浴缸的水龍頭出水才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.94,0:16:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是剛才柯南打開開關的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水卻從蓮蓬頭出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.35,0:16:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而不是從水龍頭裡出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.35,0:16:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是為什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.15,0:16:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為兇手用蓮蓬頭放水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.65,0:16:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就不至於發出很大的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.16,0:17:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他先用膠帶把麗花小姐固定在浴缸裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.76,0:17:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等時間一到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.06,0:17:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她就自然而然地溺死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.97,0:17:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一枝他也許用安眠藥什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.97,0:17:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓十點鐘從二樓下來的麗花昏睡過去後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.04,0:17:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就把她搬到浴室裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.24,0:17:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實施了剛才我說的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.44,0:17:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了讓她能在早上五點到六點之間溺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.35,0:17:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要調整水流量就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.55,0:17:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後在五點到六點的那段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.55,0:17:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他只要和我們一起留在客廳裡就能製造不在場證明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.35,0:17:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了七點以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.56,0:17:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他假裝上廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.16,0:17:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把已經溺死的麗花小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.86,0:17:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從浴缸裡面拉出來就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.96,0:17:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是僅僅如此的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.86,0:17:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種幼稚的手法很容易被識破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.06,0:17:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以他馬上埋下伏筆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.87,0:17:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伏筆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.77,0:17:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.87,0:17:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他攻擊小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.67,0:17:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為的就是讓我們認為麗花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.04,0:17:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是被硬壓到水裡溺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.44,0:17:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是這種犯罪手法的缺陷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.95,0:17:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是被他固定在浴缸裡的麗花小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.15,0:17:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很有可能被別人事先發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.65,0:17:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以他事先把那裡附近的燈破壞掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.86,0:18:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我們都在另一邊活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.96,0:18:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為如果被人發現的話計畫就失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.96,0:18:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一枝也注意到了這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.96,0:18:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以他才特地親自去查看浴缸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.57,0:18:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.27,0:18:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.17,0:18:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能用這種手法犯案的就是一枝先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.94,0:18:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了你之外沒有別人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.94,0:18:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這個手法真的行得通的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.95,0:18:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最可疑的確實是我沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.95,0:18:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點我承認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你真的親眼看到了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.75,0:18:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,親眼看到我殺人了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.06,0:18:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒有證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.96,0:18:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做出這種異想天開的推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.66,0:18:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實在太荒謬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.26,0:18:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是因為這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.56,0:18:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才要你們把外套脫掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.16,0:18:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你就快點檢查我們的外套吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.07,0:18:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看你根本什麼證據都找不出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.57,0:18:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其是我想看的並不是你們的外套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.74,0:18:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是看你們的襯衫上所沾到的水漬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.64,0:18:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五條先生袖口上的水漬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.25,0:19:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是他去洗手間洗手的時候沾到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.05,0:19:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三船先生領口的小漬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.45,0:19:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是洗臉的時候沾到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.16,0:19:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你身上的水漬是怎麼弄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.96,0:19:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會在兩個手肘的位置沾到水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.16,0:19:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這...這個和他們兩個一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.66,0:19:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是洗手的時候沾到的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.75,0:19:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.16,0:19:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼是洗臉的時候弄到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.05,0:19:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.45,0:19:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不把外套脫掉的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.67,0:19:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個地方是不可能沾到水的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.94,0:19:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有錯 之前你曾經把外套脫掉過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.44,0:19:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你必須把當時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.04,0:19:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全浸在水裡的麗花小姐搬到浴缸外面來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.45,0:19:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的袖口沒濕手肘卻濕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因為你把袖子捲起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.45,0:19:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣吧 一枝先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.75,0:19:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.76,0:19:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是他為什麼要這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.46,0:19:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次的被害人全部都是溺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.36,0:19:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依我判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.36,0:19:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這恐怕和兩年前八重子那件意外有關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.37,0:19:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八重子才不是因為意外死亡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.97,0:19:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是被殺掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.37,0:19:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是被二階堂和麗花殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.84,0:20:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那天在大暴雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.34,0:20:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八重子為了去救被困的麗花小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.44,0:20:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,划著橡皮艇到島上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.65,0:20:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她自己身上穿著救生衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.15,0:20:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同時把給麗花穿的救生衣也放在橡皮艇裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.95,0:20:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是八重子到了島上就大吃一驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.65,0:20:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為除了麗花之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.16,0:20:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二階堂也被困在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.36,0:20:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是救生衣只有兩件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.46,0:20:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.66,0:20:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.97,0:20:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是他們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.07,0:20:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把八重子的救生衣搶走才因此得救的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.27,0:20:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是他們對於去救他們的八重子卻見死不救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.54,0:20:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就覺得不對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.14,0:20:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八重子被發現的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.14,0:20:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該穿在她身上的救生衣卻沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.94,0:20:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們兩個在得救之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.35,0:20:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻說根本沒看到八重子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.65,0:20:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是事實不一定就是你想像的這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.75,0:20:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在殺掉他們之前我已經都問過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.66,0:20:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們也都承認了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.66,0:20:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們就這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.16,0:20:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把我最心愛的八重子給殺死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.46,0:20:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們是死有餘辜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.27,0:20:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二階堂和這個女人都該死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.37,0:21:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不要胡說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.44,0:21:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米嬸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.34,0:21:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個世界上沒有什麼人是該死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.04,0:21:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並不是說我已經原諒了大小姐以前犯的錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.75,0:21:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是不管什麼人死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.15,0:21:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都一定會有人傷心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.46,0:21:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要我一個人受這樣的罪就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.66,0:21:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要我一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.35,0:23:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小蘭妳也被攻擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.26,0:23:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時候我喝了安眠藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.96,0:23:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以不是記得很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.17,0:23:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是那個時候有種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.47,0:23:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是新一他來救我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.95,0:23:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.44,0:23:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是新一他根本就沒有到那個別墅去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.94,0:23:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實來救我的人是柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.95,0:23:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以那一定是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.05,0:23:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.35,0:23:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像他那樣的推理狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.95,0:23:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.35,0:23:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個大笨蛋怎麼可能那麼聰明呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.16,0:23:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂 你們說得也太過份了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.77,0:23:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒救了 他已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.94,0:23:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是誰幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.44,0:23:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然當著我的面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.14,0:23:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.24,0:23:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.64,0:23:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.25,0:24:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.65,0:24:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你終於回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.95,0:24:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.26,0:24:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.56,0:24:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡拉OK包廂殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.86,0:24:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.47,0:24:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅鼻子的馴鹿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.07,0:24:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次的事件發生在卡拉OK包廂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.07,0:24:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 把麥克風還給我啦
